    "description": "<p>The purpose of the dtata management plan (DMP) is to contribute to good data handling by describing what<br>research data the project expects to use, data handling principles, and an assessment<br>of what data can be shared with the public or why data cannot be open. Furthermore, it<br>gives instructions on naming conventions and metadata structure.</p>",
